snippet.title: Pier Solar Official Trailer
snippet.description:
This is the official trailer for Pier Solar and the Great Architects.

Pier Solar will be released on September 30th, 2014 for PS4, PS3, STEAM, and OUYA.

For more information, visit:
www.magicalgamefactory.com
